<br>
Woon speaks the truth, although I'd add Cursed in there too. And Emp is the only fight in the game right now Id say you *need* 2 Mages unless you have over 8-10 Clerics, although now that my gear/FT is really getting up there, I think you could squeak by with 1 and a dedicated healer.<br>
<br>
As you get higher end gear and more AA, Mage slip into their role real well I think. The initial shock from going full offense to mostly utility with some offense, I can understand how some feel, I know I did at the time.<br>
<br>
For the past week or so Ive been the sole Mage for all the fights in VT, and it really isn't that bad. Debuffing, nuking, pet, rods, focus items, cohs. We may not be full offense, but we defintely bring a lot to a raid, and it's more than just dropping rods.<br>
